data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience with this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence situated at 1420 N Ave C in the heart of Denver city. Nestled on a corner lot, this home boasts a prime location overlooking a picturesque park and the city pool. The property offers a spacious layout featuring two inviting living areas, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment. With its thoughtfully designed floor plan, this home presents a seamless flow that combines functionality and style. Inside, you'll find three well appointed bedrooms and two bathrooms. The corner lot setting provides a sense of space and privacy, while the proximity to the park and city pool ensures endless recreational opportunities right at your doorstep. This residence offers not only a comfortable living space but also a strategic location that grants easy access to local amenities, shops, and dining options. Don't miss your chance to make this house your home!
